      <hedline>
        <hl1>Pampered Toes</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Chesterfield Mayfair hotel in London offers Shop in the Lap of Luxury package which includes private foot massage each day, Champagne, full English breakfast and shopping vouchers (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Dedicated shoppers know what a great source of exercise browsing and buying is. But it has its downside. For that, the Chesterfield Mayfair, a London hotel, offers a package with a private foot massage each day called Shop in the Lap of Luxury. It also comes with a bottle of Champagne, a full English breakfast and about $37 in shopping vouchers. It costs $265, double, the first night and $235 each night after that, plus 17.5 percent V.A.T. Valid Nov. 1 to Dec. 28. The 110-room hotel is at 35 Charles Street, just off Berkeley Square; (44-207) 491-2622.</p>
      </block>
